<DOCNO> NYT20000213.0016 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-13 15:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5544 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      02-13 0870
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE>
(HLW) 
</HEADLINE>
 AM-NYT-BUDGET
<TEXT>
<P>
