quickly become `Straussed out' by the waltz music you will hear in
every restaurant, coffee house and concert hall.'' Actually, we
have a high tolerance for Johann Strauss. But we were very nearly
``Worn Out by Wolfgang.''
</P>
<P>
   By John Owen. (Story has moved in the ``d'' category.)
