Gordon, who plays the victim of nerve gas in a simulated attack on
a Latham gymnasium. The Pentagon is forming 27 of these groups,
called Weapons of Mass Destruction Civilian Support Teams, which
fall under the command of the state National Guards and are
assigned to zones established by the Federal Emergency Management
Agency. (James Estrin/The New York Times)
